{
  "message": "test(fuzz): extend fuzz_common_dtype corpus with 18 dtype pair seeds\n\nAdd structured corpus seeds for dtype coercion symmetry testing:\n- Same-type pairs: Null-Null, Bool-Bool, Int64-Int64, Float64-Float64, Utf8-Utf8\n- Null with all types: Null-Bool, Null-Int64, Null-Float64, Null-Utf8\n- Numeric promotions: Bool-Int64, Bool-Float64, Int64-Float64\n- Incompatible pairs: Bool-Utf8, Int64-Utf8, Float64-Utf8\n- Reverse pairs: Float64-Bool, Float64-Int64, Utf8-Null\n\nIncludes batch unit test that replays all 18 seeds through the harness.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.5 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
  "files": [
